00:43:09,670 --> 00:43:13,080
During the Song Dynasty, fragrance culture reached its peak.

832
00:43:13,910 --> 00:43:16,950
Incense became a beloved element in the lives of Song people.

833
00:43:17,430 --> 00:43:18,230
In the Song Dynasty,

834
00:43:18,230 --> 00:43:21,080
