835
00:43:21,080 --> 00:43:22,040
the Fourfold Noble Incense.

836
00:43:22,040 --> 00:43:23,160
[Agarwood, sandalwood, borneol, musk]

837
00:43:23,180 --> 00:43:24,950
It was made using agarwood, sandalwood, borneol, and musk,

838
00:43:24,950 --> 00:43:27,910
four extremely expensive ingredients.

839
00:43:28,190 --> 00:43:29,320
So, can you guess

840
00:43:29,430 --> 00:43:32,430
how much it cost to buy a single

841
00:43:32,430 --> 00:43:34,150
Fourfold Noble Incense in Bianjing?

842
00:43:34,470 --> 00:43:36,390
A single liang of Fourfold Noble Incense

843
00:43:37,000 --> 00:43:38,230
would take this tea stall's

844
00:43:38,230 --> 00:43:41,120
