845
00:43:41,280 --> 00:43:42,150
That expensive?

846
00:44:05,540 --> 00:44:07,100
Freezing rain lingers for months

847
00:44:07,340 --> 00:44:08,940
Followed by cold snow

848
00:44:09,180 --> 00:44:10,500
Through boiling waters and raging flames

849
00:44:10,740 --> 00:44:13,100
Chase eastward along the Bian River

850
00:44:13,300 --> 00:44:15,140
Time flows day by day, month by month

851
00:44:15,500 --> 00:44:17,420
Feign joy with drinks before the camps

852
00:44:17,860 --> 00:44:18,820
Stagger home after the drinking games

853
00:44:18,940 --> 00:44:19,820
Such is the state of the world

854
00:44:20,020 --> 00:44:21,660
In the years of displacement

855
00:44:22,300 --> 00:44:25,060
Heads are bowed to the ground in poverty

856
00:44:26,580 --> 00:44:29,500
